    {
      "id": "PopularPost342906",
      "post_content": "Unfortunately the worst of the cycle, since the time delay doesn't play nice with the discard (although if it's timed so it hits your opponent's last two cards that's actually pretty nasty). An amusing note is that if [Zur the Enchanter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zur the Enchanter) already has three +1/+1 counters on him, you can have quite a bit of fun with these.  \n  \nAlso interesting: You get the benefit regardless of who controls the creature. Thus, enchanting a buffed up enemy creature can actually be an effective deterrent.",
      "posted_by": "LordRandomness",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost342906\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Unfortunately the worst of the cycle, since the time delay doesn't play nice with the discard (although if it's timed so it hits your opponent's last two cards that's actually pretty nasty). An amusing note is that if <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Zur the Enchanter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Zur the Enchanter\">Zur the Enchanter</a> already has three +1/+1 counters on him, you can have quite a bit of fun with these.<br/><br/>Also interesting: You get the benefit regardless of who controls the creature. Thus, enchanting a buffed up enemy creature can actually be an effective deterrent.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '342906'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy76236\">LordRandomness</span>\r\n                                (9/24/2013 3:07:46 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starR